  "title": "DRIVER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Packing, loading and unloading delivery vans and trucks</li><li>Utilizing navigation apps to find the most optimal route.</li><li>Working at night and on weekends.</li><li>Maintaining an organized travel schedule.</li><li>Ensuring that vehicles have sufficient gas and are always ready for use.</li><li>Carrying out vehicle maintenance checks.</li><li>Arranging for vehicle repairs when necessary.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>A valid driver's license.</li><li>Extensive knowledge of the operating area.</li><li>Excellent organizational and time management skills.</li><li>Proficiency using GPS devices.</li><li>Able to work on night shift / weekend and public holidays.</li></ul>",
